@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_urzeip(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.exp(0.96))
    v0 = v1
    v1 = (0.41 / ((v1 + 0.52 / v0 + 0.38) * v0))
    v0 = (v2 / wp.cos(wp.exp(v2 + 0.63)))
    tmp = wp.cos(v1)
    v0 = 0.39
    data[tid] = v0
